  AppCache -->|"new grids"| MapView`],images:[]},{id:"kickgoing-town-map",name:"동네지도",meta:"2022.07 – 2022.12 · Mobile · TypeScript",tags:["platform:ios","platform:android","lang:ts"],desc:{en:"Place-based social map feature — brings users into the app even when not renting a scooter. Users discover and tag nearby locations using emoji markers on the Naver Map.",ko:"장소 기반 SNS 기능 — 킥보드를 사용하지 않아도 앱에 들어오게 하는 신규 경험. Naver Map 위에 이모지 마커로 주변 장소를 발견하고 태그할 수 있음."},role:{en:"Responsible for emoji picker, custom Naver Map info-window (Native Bridge modification), collapsible panel animation (Reanimated + Pan Gesture), rendering and location-call optimization, and API service layer redesign.",ko:"이모지 피커, Naver Map 말풍선 커스터마이징(Native Bridge 수정), 접이식 패널 애니메이션(Reanimated + Pan Gesture), 렌더링·위치 조회 최적화, API 서비스 레이어 재설계 담당."},achievement:{en:"No suitable open-source emoji picker existed — surveyed the Unicode emoji specification, understood the dataset structure, built a custom picker from scratch, and published two npm packages: ts-unicode-emojis (emoji dataset utility) and react-native-emoji-collection-view (the picker component). Extended react-native-naver-map's Native Bridge view to support custom info-window (call-out balloon) rendering. Built a collapsible bottom panel with Reanimated and Pan Gesture: it had to compose with existing bottom UI and behave differently across multiple scenarios, so a gesture-driven reusable Animated.View was the only viable approach. Performance degraded with the new Lottie-heavy UI — Flipper Profiler identified the cause as continuous location polling and API calls even when the map was off-screen; resolved by deduplicating calls and restricting location updates to active-rental and visible-map states. Redesigned the API service layer: replaced scattered inline URL construction and get/post calls with a typed service that auto-converts snake_case↔camelCase; injected Redux dispatch into services so any module can read/write Redux state without being a Redux function.",ko:"적합한 오픈소스 이모지 피커가 없어 유니코드 이모지 규격을 분석·구조 파악 후 직접 구현, ts-unicode-emojis(이모지 데이터셋 유틸리티)·react-native-emoji-collection-view(피커 컴포넌트) 두 개의 npm 패키지로 배포. react-native-naver-map Native Bridge View 수정해 커스텀 말풍선(InfoWindow) 렌더링 지원 추가. Reanimated + Pan Gesture로 접이식 하단 패널 직접 구현 — 기존 하단 UI와 결합 및 시나리오별 다른 동작이 필요해 재사용 가능한 Gesture 기반 Animated View로 설계. Lottie 포함 신규 UI에서 성능 저하 발생 — Flipper Profiler로 지도 비활성 상태에서도 위치 조회·API 호출이 지속됨을 특정, 중복 제거 및 대여 중·지도 활성 상태에서만 위치 조회하도록 수정. API 서비스 레이어 재설계: 로직 내 URL 직접 생성·get/post 분산 호출을 타입 완비 서비스로 교체, snake_case↔camelCase 자동 변환, Redux dispatch 주입으로 Redux 함수 외부에서도 스토어 접근 가능하게 구현."},tech:["TypeScript","React Native","Reanimated","Pan Gesture","Lottie","Flipper","Naver Map"],image:null,links:[{label:"GitHub: ts-unicode-emojis",href:"https://github.com/2sem/ts-unicode-emojis"},{label:"GitHub: react-native-emoji-collection-view",href:"https://github.com/2sem/react-native-emoji-collection-view"},{label:"Medium: Debugging RN with Flipper",href:"https://medium.com/@toyboy2/debugging-react-native-with-flipper-262da7bcadc7"},{label:"Medium: Resizing RN View with Pan Gesture",href:"https://toyboy2.medium.com/resizing-react-native-view-with-pan-gesture-2e19db93238e"}],diagrams:[`flowchart TD
